# Account info
IMAPAccount gawmk-gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User mikolaj.gawrys@gmail.com
PassCmd "cat ~/.google-app-pass"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt


# Remote storage
IMAPStore gawmk-gmail-remote
Account gawmk-gmail


# Local storage
MaildirStore gawmk-gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/gawmk-gmail/ 
Inbox ~/mail/gawmk-gmail/Inbox


Channel gawmk-gmail
Near :gawmk-gmail-local:
Far :gawmk-gmail-remote:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/Sent Mail" "[Gmail]/Starred" "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Bin"
Create Both
SyncState *